data.description: Discover the allure of PARKVIEW ESTATES in the vibrant heart of South Fort Worth, surrounded by the excellence of Crowley ISD. This single-story residence unveils the captivating Camden floor plan with an elevation of c, showcasing a modern and open concept. The kitchen beckons with its ample cabinetry, a convenient sitting island, electric range, and a walk-in pantry. A bright dining area seamlessly transitions to a spacious living room, perfect for family gatherings. The main bedroom offers a luxurious escape with a 5-foot oversized shower and a generously sized walk-in closet. With the added convenience of Connected Smart Home Technology, step outside to the covered back patio and enjoy the privacy of the fenced backyard. This home is ideally located, providing easy access to I-35W, Chisholm Trail Tollway, Bicentennial Park playground, walking trails, Hulen Mall, The Shops at Clearfork, and more. Embrace comfort and style in this well-connected abode at PARKVIEW ESTATES.
